        <item>
            <title>Diablo 4 將登陸 Steam Deck 最快本月 17 號有得玩</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/15/diablo-4-2/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=diablo-4-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/15/diablo-4-2/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 02:31:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[diablo 4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[steam]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[steam deck]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[暴雪]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1199242</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">有遊戲網站透露，指《Diablo 4》已通過 Steam Deck 的認證，意味著玩家最快可在幾日後在 Steam Deck 遊玩《Diablo 4》。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1199250 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/F8Qe08zWwAAr3sJ.png" alt="" width="685" height="381" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《Diablo 4》已通過 Steam Deck 的認證</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">上星期暴雪宣佈《Diablo 4》將會在 10 月 17 日在 Steam 上正式推出，當時有玩家期待會遊戲會否可在 Steam Deck 裏運行，疑問在一星期後被解答。暴雪社羣發展總監 Adam Fletcher 在 X 上指暴雪已經確認《Diablo 4》從發布之日起將通過 Steam Deck 驗證，即最快可在 10 月 17 日，發布的第一天起就可在在 Steam Deck 上正常運行。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1199249 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-13-at-6.40.25-PM-694x425.png" alt="" width="694" height="425" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-13-at-6.40.25-PM-694x425.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-13-at-6.40.25-PM-768x470.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-13-at-6.40.25-PM.png 1196w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲暴雪社羣發展總監 Adam Fletcher</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">獲得 Steam Deck 驗證對於 Steam Deck 用戶來説是個好消息，他們無需使用第三方應用程式。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/PezRadar/status/1712525922400895457?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1712525922400895457%7Ctwgr%5E4387154e0b1b5ea92961afe5988f7285e87d5fee%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamereactor.cn%2Fdiablo-iv-will-be-steam-deck-verified-from-day-one-620963%2F">Adam Fletcher‘s X</a></p><p>圖片來源：<span class="css-901oao css-16my406 r-poiln3 r-bcqeeo r-qvutc0">Wario64’s X</span></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
